","description":"A glacial expanse in Orgoreyn, contiguous with the Pering Ice during winter storms.","recentEvents":"Mentioned as a geographical counterpart to the Pering Ice, part of the frozen north.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Ice","relationship":"Contiguous during winter"}]},{"name":"Shath Domain","aliases":["Hearth of Shath"],"description":"A Karhidish domain where the tragic tale of Getheren and Hode originated.","recentEvents":"The brothers' broken vow and Getheren's exile began here, leading to his journey north.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Storm-border","relationship":"Historical location tied to the brothers' story"}]},{"name":"Orgoreyn","aliases":["Karhide's neighbor"],"arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"A rival state to Karhide, known for its harsh environment and political tensions.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai contemplates traveling here but hesitates due to potential difficulties returning to Karhide.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Adjacent rival state"}]},{"name":"Fastnesses","arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"A remote eastern region of Karhide containing the Foretellers, who hold significant cultural and prophetic influence.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai resolves to travel here to gather information about Karhide's political dynamics.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Eastern region"}]},{"name":"Grende","aliases":["Grende Region"],"description":"A region in northern Osnoriner, home to Charuthe.","recentEvents":"Herbor travels through the snows of Grende on his way to Charuthe to seek a foretelling for Berosty rem ir Ipe.","relationships":[{"location":"Charuthe","relationship":"Adjacent region"}]},{"name":"New Port","aliases":["New Port"],"description":"A coastal city serving as a departure point for caravans heading east.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai departs from here aboard a trade-caravan bound for the Pering Storm-border.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Storm-border","relationship":"Part of the caravan's route"}]},{"name":"Eskar Pass","aliases":["Eskar Pass"],"description":"A mountain pass through the Kargav range, critical for caravan travel.","recentEvents":"The caravan traverses this pass, encountering extreme weather and avalanches.","relationships":[{"location":"Kargav","relationship":"A key route through the mountain range"}]},{"name":"Ariskostor Fastness","aliases":["Ariskostor Fastness"],"description":"A remote castle-like structure perched on the Kargav's southern face.","recentEvents":"The driver describes it as a residence for the Old Men, inaccessible for most of the year.","relationships":[{"location":"Kargav","relationship":"Located on the mountain range"}]},{"name":"Otherhord","aliases":["Otherhord"],"arc":"Gethenian Cultural Exploration","description":"A secluded Fastness in a forested region, home to the Handdara cult.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai stays here to study the Foretellers' practices and their philosophy of nusuth.","relationships":[{"location":"Fastnesses","relationship":"A specific example of a Handdara retreat"}]},{"name":"Spreve","description":"Domain of the physician from Spreve, a region known for its medical expertise and connection to the Foretellers.","recentEvents":"The physician from Spreve entered the Foretelling circle during the session, interrupting the ritual with a demand for light.","relationships":[{"location":"Otherhord","relationship":"The physician's origin domain"}]}],"arcs":[{"name":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","status":"active","characters":["Genly Ai","King Argaven XV","Pemmer Harge rem ir Tibe"],"summary":"Ai continues his journey toward the Fastnesses, navigating the caravan's perilous route across the Kargav mountains while reflecting on Karhide's political tensions and the potential for war with Orgoreyn."},{"name":"Estraven's Exile and Political Labyrinth","status":"active","characters":["Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","King Argaven XV"],"summary":"Ai's suspicions about Estraven's exile deepen, questioning whether Estraven lied to him or if the king's political maneuvering has shifted, with Estraven now forced into exile."},{"name":"Gethenian Cultural Exploration","status":"active","characters":["Genly Ai","Weaver Odren","Faxe the Weaver"],"summary":"Ai immerses himself in the Handdara cult's practices at Otherhord, observing the Foretellers' enigmatic rituals and the philosophy of nusuth, deepening his understanding of Gethenian culture and its contrast to Terran norms."}],"summary":"Genly Ai undergoes a Foretelling session in Otherhord, learning that Gethen will join the Ekumen in five years. The ritual reveals the complexities of prophecy, with the Weaver Faxe emphasizing the role of uncertainty and the Handdara's rejection of deterministic answers. The session ends in chaos, highlighting the tension between knowledge and ignorance that defines the Handdara's philosophy."},"model":"qwen3:8b","appVersion":"0.1.0"},{"index":9,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Genly Ai","aliases":["Mr. Ai","the Envoy"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"6. One Way into Orgoreyn","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The Ekumen's Envoy to Karhide, struggling with the political and psychological complexities of his mission.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Former contact; Estraven is now the King’s Ear"},{"character":"King Argaven XV","relationship":"The monarch he is attempting to persuade to join the Ekumen"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed the Envoy's request to enter Orgoreyn, his role in Karhide's politics, and the implications of interstellar communication."},{"name":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","aliases":["The King’s Ear","Lord Estraven"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"6. One Way into Orgoreyn","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The king's trusted advisor exiled for allegedly conspiring to undermine Karhide's sovereignty.","relationships":[{"character":"King Argaven XV","relationship":"Formerly the king's closest confidant and advisor"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Distrustful contact with ambiguous motives"}],"recentEvents":"Conveyed the Envoy's request to enter Orgoreyn, debated the implications of interstellar diplomacy, and warned of Karhide's internal threats."},{"name":"King Argaven XV","aliases":["the king"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"Royal House","description":"The paranoid and volatile ruler of Karhide, suspicious of foreign influence and internal dissent.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Formerly his most trusted advisor, now exiled"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"The Envoy whose mission he resists and interrogates"}],"recentEvents":"Mentioned in context of Karhide’s political climate"},{"name":"Pemmer Harge rem ir Tibe","aliases":["the king’s cousin"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The king’s cousin and a member of the upper chamber, known for his rivalry with Estraven.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Rival and political adversary"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Interacted during the dinner conversation"}],"recentEvents":"Featured in news about Karhide’s territorial claims in the Sinoth Valley"},{"name":"servant","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1. A Parade in Erhenrang","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A Karhidish servant who left after the meal.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Departed to their home after the meal, as Karhiders do not employ bonded labor."},{"name":"Getheren","aliases":["Ennoch"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"2. The Place Inside the Blizzard","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Brother who survived the exile and journey to the Ice, met his brother Hode in the Place Inside the Blizzard.","relationships":[{"character":"Hode","relationship":"Brother"}],"recentEvents":"Traveled to the Pering Ice, encountered Hode, died after returning to Shath and revealing his identity."},{"name":"Hode","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"2. The Place Inside the Blizzard","currentLocation":"The Place Inside the Blizzard","description":"Getheren's brother who committed suicide after being exiled, now resides in the Place Inside the Blizzard.","relationships":[{"character":"Getheren","relationship":"Brother"}],"recentEvents":"Died by suicide, appeared to Getheren in the Place Inside the Blizzard as a white, lifeless figure."},{"name":"the traveler","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"2. The Place Inside the Blizzard","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Carried Getheren's message back to Shath, confirming the domain's recovery after Getheren's death.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Received Getheren's final message and relayed it to Shath, contributing to the domain's restoration."},{"name":"Lord Berosty rem ir Ipe","aliases":["Ashe Berosty rem ir Ipe"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"4. The Nineteenth Day","currentLocation":"Grende","description":"A nobleman who sought a Foretelling about his death and later killed his kemmering Herbor before dying by suicide.","relationships":[{"character":"Herbor of the Geganner clan","relationship":"kemmering"}],"recentEvents":"Received a Foretelling about his death, killed Herbor, and hanged himself on Odstreth."},{"name":"Herbor of the Geganner clan","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"4. The Nineteenth Day","currentLocation":"Grende","description":"A poor man who sought a Foretelling to save his kemmering Berosty rem ir Ipe.","relationships":[{"character":"Lord Berosty rem ir Ipe","relationship":"kemmering"}],"recentEvent