cal significance. A monumental structure completed to enhance Erhenrang's trade and infrastructure. A communal living space for foreigners in Erhenrang, where Genly Ai resides.","recentEvents":"Hosted a parade celebrating the completion of the Arch of the River Gate, where Genly Ai interacts with key figures like King Argaven XV and Therem Harth rem ir Estraven.; Central to the parade, with the king and masons participating in its final assembly.; Where Genly Ai reflects on his isolation and observes local customs.","relationships":[{"location":"Royal House","relationship":"Contains the royal residence and administrative center"},{"location":"Palace of Erhenrang","relationship":"Part of the city's walled inner complex"}]},{"name":"Royal House","aliases":["King's Residence","Royal Palace"],"arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"The fortified palace complex housing the king and key political figures.","recentEvents":"Served as the backdrop for the royal procession and the keystone-laying ceremony.","relationships":[{"location":"Erhenrang","relationship":"Central structure within the city"},{"location":"King's House","relationship":"Part of the same complex"}]},{"name":"Corner Red Dwelling","aliases":["Estraven's Home"],"arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"A historic residence of Therem Harth rem ir Estraven, symbolizing his political influence.","recentEvents":"Where Genly Ai is invited for dinner, revealing shifting power dynamics.","relationships":[{"location":"Erhenrang","relationship":"Located within the city's walls"}]},{"name":"Winter","aliases":["Planet Winter","Gethen"],"description":"The icy planet where Karhide is located, with extreme seasonal variations.","recentEvents":"Setting for the entire narrative, with Genly Ai navigating its harsh climate and politics.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Nation on the planet"}]},{"name":"Old Bridge","aliases":["Ancient Bridge"],"description":