n on the Farm","currentLocation":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","description":"A former carpenter imprisoned at the farm, known for his storytelling and eventual death from illness.","relationships":[{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Prisoner companion"}],"recentEvents":"Engaged in conversations with Genly Ai about his past, died after falling into a coma."},{"name":"the guards","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"13. Down on the Farm","currentLocation":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","description":"Probationary prisoners overseeing the farm's operations.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Monitored prisoners and administered examinations."},{"name":"Commissioner Shusgis","aliases":["Shusgis"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"10. Conversations in Mishnory","currentLocation":"Mishnory","description":"Coerced into providing information about the Sarf by Genly Ai.","relationships":[{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Provided information about Sarf and political factions"}],"recentEvents":"Discussed Orgoreyn's secret police, Estraven's status, and political factions"},{"name":"Sardon rem ir Chene-wich","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Royal Embassy","description":"Former court acquaintance who conveyed a message to King Argaven.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Helped Genly Ai communicate with King Argaven"},{"name":"Mavriva","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Old man who led the hunting party in the Esagel region.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Guided Estraven's escape route through the wilderness"},{"name":"the skiers","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Skiers encountered by Estraven during his escape.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Briefly interacted with Estraven before continuing their journey"}],"locations":[{"name":"Erhenrang","aliases":["Capital City","City of Karhide","Arch of the River Gate","New Road and River Port","Island","Genly's Lodgings","Winter","Planet Winter","Gethen","Old Bridge","Ancient Bridge"],"arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"The capital city of Karhide, known for its grand architecture and political significance. A monumental structure completed to enhance Erhenrang's trade and infrastructure. A communal living space for foreigners in Erhenrang, where Genly Ai resides. The icy planet where Karhide is located, with extreme seasonal variations. A historic bridge over the river, noted for its arches and traditional construction methods.","recentEvents":"Hosted a parade celebrating the completion of the Arch of the River Gate, where Genly Ai interacts with key figures like King Argaven XV and Therem Harth rem ir Estraven.; Central to the parade, with the king and masons participating in its final assembly.; Where Genly Ai reflects on his isolation and observes local customs.; Setting for the entire narrative, with Genly Ai navigating its harsh climate and politics.; Mentioned as a reference point for the arch's mortar techniques.","relationships":[{"location":"Royal House","relationship":"Contains the royal residence and administrative center"},{"location":"Palace of Erhenrang","relationship":"Part of the city's walled inner complex"}]},{"name":"Royal House","aliases":["King's Residence","Royal Palace"],"arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Karhide-Orgoreyn Temporal Tensions","description":"The fortified palace complex housing the king and key political figures.","recentEvents":"Served as the backdrop for the royal procession and the keystone-laying ceremony.","relationships":[{"location":"Erhenrang","relationship":"Central structure within the city"},{"location":"King's House","relationship":"Part of the same complex"}]},{"name":"Corner Red Dwelling","aliases":["Estraven's Home"],"arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"A historic residence of Therem Harth rem ir Estraven, symbolizing his political influence.","recentEvents":"Where Genly Ai is invited for dinner, revealing shifting power dynamics.","relationships":[{"location":"Erhenrang","relationship":"Located within the city's walls"}]},{"name":"Sess Embankment","aliases":["River Embankment"],"description":"A public area along the river where crowds gather for events.","recentEvents":"Where the parade crowd watches the keystone ceremony and the king's procession.","relationships":[{"location":"Erhenrang","relationship":"Key public space in the city"}],"parentLocation":"Erhenrang"},{"name":"Karhide","aliases":["Nation of Karhide"],"arc":"Estraven's Exile and Cross-National Political Strategies","description":"A politically complex nation on Winter, ruled by King Argaven XV.","recentEvents":"Central to the narrative, with Genly Ai navigating its social and political structures.","relationships":[{"location":"Winter","relationship":"Nation on the planet"}]},{"name":"North Fall","aliases":["High North Fall"],"description":"A remote, snowbound region bordering Karhide and Orgoreyn, marked by harsh climate and political tension.","recentEvents":"Estraven discusses aiding Karhidish farmers displaced from the Sinoth Valley, risking political fallout with the king.","relationships":[{"location":"Sassinoth Valley","relationship":"Adjacent border region contested by Karhide and Orgoreyn"},{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Part of Karhide's northern territory"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Sassinoth Valley","aliases":["Sinoth Valley"],"arc":"Estraven's Political Maneuvering and Border Dispute (Historical Context)","description":"A valley trapped in political conflict between Karhide and Orgoreyn, where the narrative's central tensions unfold.","recentEvents":"Karhidish farmers launched a foray here, burning an Orgota village and dumping bodies into the Ey River.","relationships":[{"location":"North Fall","relationship":"Part of the contested border region"},{"location":"Orgoreyn","relationship":"Historically inhabited by Orgoreyn settlers"},{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Site of political resistance to the Envoy's mission"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Remny Tower","description":"A tower in Erhenrang where gongs mark the time, symbolizing the city's rigid temporal structure.","recentEvents":"Estraven and Genly Ai hear the gongs signaling midnight as their conversation concludes.","relationships":[{"location":"Erhenrang","relationship":"Part of the city's infrastructure"}],"parentLocation":"Erhenrang"},{"name":"Pering Storm-border","aliases":["Storm-border"],"description":"A region in northern Karhide bordering the Pering Ice, known for its harsh climate and the tragic tale of Getheren and Hode.","recentEvents":"The brothers Getheren and Hode vowed kemmering, but their vow was broken after Getheren's brother committed suicide, leading Getheren to flee northward.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Ice","relationship":"Adjacent region"},{"location":"Shath Domain","relationship":"Historical location tied to the brothers' story"}]},{"name":"Pering Ice","aliases":["Pering Glacier"],"description":"A vast glacial sheet covering northern Karhide, contiguous with the Gobrin Ice of Orgoreyn during winter.","recentEvents":"Getheren traveled northward across the Ice, encountering a supernatural realm where the dead dwell.","relationships":[{"location":"Gobrin Ice","relationship":"Contiguous during winter"},{"location":"The Place Inside the Blizzard","relationship":"Site of Getheren's encounter with Hode"}]},{"name":"The Place Inside the Blizzard","aliases":["Blizzard Place"],"description":"A supernatural realm existing within the Pering Ice, where the dead who died in kemmering dwell eternally.","recentEvents":"Getheren met his deceased brother Hode here, who could not speak his name due to his death.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Ice","relationship":"Located within the glacier"},{"location":"Shath Domain","relationship":"Linked to the brothers' tragic history"}],"parentLocation":"Pering Ice"},{"name":"Gobrin Glacier","aliases":["Great Glacier","Ice-sheet","The Ice","The Gobrin Ice","Gobrin Ice"],"description":"A vast, unbroken expanse of ice stretching to the horizon, formed by millennia of glacial movement across the northern reaches of Gethen.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai and Estraven reach the glacier after traversing the Sembensyens Mountains, overcoming harsh weather and physical exhaustion. The glacier's sheer scale and beauty mark the culmination of their journey.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Ice","relationship":"Contiguous during winter"},{"location":"Fire-Hills","relationship":"Adjacent to the glacier, visible from the plateau"},{"location":"Sembensyens Mountains","relationship":"The glacier lies beyond the mountain range's northern extremity"},{"location":"Shenshey Bogs","relationship":"The final leg of their journey leads from the Ice-sheet to these frozen bogs"}],"arc":"Estraven's Exile and Cross-National Political Strategies"},{"name":"Shath Domain","aliases":["Hearth of Shath"],"description":"A Karhidish domain where the tragic tale of Getheren and Hode originated.","recentEvents":"The brothers' broken vow and Getheren's exile began here, leading to his journey north.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Storm-border","relationship":"Historical location tied to the brothers' story"}]},{"name":"Orgoreyn","aliases":["Karhide's neighbor","Orgny Fastness"],"arc":"Estraven's Exile and Cross-National Political Strategies","description":"The cold, politically volatile planet where Genly Ai and Estraven navigate power struggles between Karhide and Orgoreyn.","recentEvents":"Estraven recounts his role in orchestrating Genly's exile to Orgoreyn to protect him from assassination by Pemmer Harge rem ir Tibe.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Adjacent rival state"},{"location":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","relationship":"Target of political intrigue due to its role in Genly's hidden refuge"}]},{"name":"Fastnesses","arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Political Intrigue","description":"A remote eastern region of Karhide containing the Foretellers, who hold significant cultural and prophetic influence.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai resolves to travel here to gather information about Karhide's political dynamics.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Eastern region"}]},{"name":"Grende","aliases":["Grende Region"],"description":"A region in northern Osnoriner, home to Charuthe.","recentEvents":"Herbor travels through the snows of Grende on his way to Charuthe to seek a foretelling for Berosty rem ir Ipe.","relationships":[{"location":"Charuthe","relationship":"Adjacent region"}]},{"name":"New Port","aliases":["New Port"],"description":"A coastal city serving as a departure point for caravans heading east.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai departs from here aboard a trade-caravan bound for the Pering Storm-border.","relationships":[{"location":"Pering Storm-border","relationship":"Part of the caravan's route"}]},{"name":"Eskar Pass","aliases":["Eskar Pass"],"description":"A mountain pass through the Kargav range, critical for caravan travel.","recentEvents":"The caravan traverses this pass, encountering extreme weather and avalanches.","relationships":[{"location":"Kargav","relationship":"A key route through the mountain range"}]},{"name":"Ariskostor Fastness","aliases":["Ariskostor Fastness"],"description":"A remote castle-like structure perched on the Kargav's southern face.","recentEvents":"The driver describes it as a residence for the Old Men, inaccessible for most of the year.","relationships":[{"location":"Kargav","relationship":"Located on the mountain range"}]},{"name":"Otherhord","aliases":["Otherhord"],"arc":"Gethenian Cultural Exploration","description":"A secluded Fastness in a forested region, home to the Handdara cult.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai stays here to study the Foretellers' practices and their philosophy of nusuth.","relationships":[{"location":"Fastnesses","relationship":"A specific example of a Handdara retreat"}]},{"name":"Spreve","description":"Domain of the physician from Spreve, a region known for its medical expertise and connection to the Foretellers.","recentEvents":"The physician from Spreve entered the Foretelling circle during the session, interrupting the ritual with a demand for light.","relationships":[{"location":"Otherhord","relationship":"The physician's origin domain"}]},{"name":"Kuseben","aliases":["Kuseben"],"description":"A coastal town in Karhide where Estraven meets Ashe and attempts to flee exile.","recentEvents":"Estraven arrives in Kuseben after fleeing Erhenrang, meets Ashe, and tries to escape to Orgoreyn by sea.","relationships":[{"location":"Orgoreyn","relationship":"Bordering region; Estraven's escape route"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Shelt Port","aliases":["Shelt"],"description":"A port city in Orgoreyn where Estraven is set ashore after being intercepted by patrol.","recentEvents":"Estraven is rescued by the Kuseben Patrol and landed here, leading to his detention in the Commensal Hospital.","relationships":[{"location":"Charisune Coastal Area Four","relationship":"Adjacent coastal region"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Markets of South Mishnory","aliases":["South Mishnory Markets"],"description":"A bustling market hub in Mishnory where Estraven finds work as a landboat loader.","recentEvents":"Estraven works in the ice-houses and lodges on Fish Island, navigating Orgoreyn's social and political systems.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Central commercial district"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Fish Island","aliases":["Fish Island"],"description":"A crowded island near Mishnory's Markets where Estraven lodges with fellow workers.","recentEvents":"Estraven resides here while working in the ice-houses, enduring harsh conditions and social scrutiny.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Residential district"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Kunderer Embankment","aliases":["Kunderer Embankment"],"description":"A tree-lined area in Mishnory offering respite from the city's heat.","recentEvents":"Estraven retreats here to escape the oppressive summer heat of Mishnory.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Recreational area"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Charisune Coastal Area Four","aliases":["Charisune Coastal Area Four"],"description":"A coastal region in Orgoreyn housing the Commensal Hospital where Estraven is detained.","recentEvents":"Estraven is hospitalized here after a failed escape attempt, where he encounters the Inspector and physician.","relationships":[{"location":"Orgoreyn","relationship":"Administrative district"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Sennethny","aliases":["Sennethny"],"description":"A location within the Twenty-fourth Commensality of Orgoreyn, tied to Estraven's hospital stay.","recentEvents":"Estraven is registered as a dependent in this commensality after his hospitalization.","relationships":[{"location":"Orgoreyn","relationship":"Subdivision of the Great Commensality"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Osnoriner","aliases":["Osnoriner Region"],"description":"A region in Karhide known for its unique divorce practices and social customs.","recentEvents":"Discussed as a place where divorce exists but remarriage after divorce or death is prohibited.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Part of the Karhide region"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Perunter","aliases":["Perunter Continent"],"description":"An Antarctic continent where incest between generations is reportedly permitted, though disputed.","recentEvents":"Mentioned as a possible location with different social norms regarding incest.","relationships":[{"location":"Orgoreyn","relationship":"Adjacent or nearby region"}]},{"name":"Gorinhering","aliases":["Gorinhering Clan-Hearth"],"description":"A Clan-Hearth on Karhide's Eastern coast, built on a hill above the Hodomin Ocean.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai resided here during the summer, interacting with locals and observing Karhidish culture.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Part of the Eastern coastal region"},{"location":"Hodomin Ocean","relationship":"Surrounded by the eternal fogs of this ocean"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Ey River","description":"A glacier-fed border river between Karhide and Orgoreyn, marked by a bridge connecting Passerer and Siuwensin.","recentEvents":"A Karhidish foray raided Siuwensin, prompting Genly's journey into Orgoreyn.","relationships":[{"location":"Passerer","relationship":"Karhidish village across the river"},{"location":"Siuwensin","relationship":"Orgota village across the river"}]},{"name":"Passerer","description":"A Karhidish village on the Karhide side of the Ey River bridge.","recentEvents":"A foray from Passerer raids Siuwensin, causing widespread destruction.","relationships":[{"location":"Ey River","relationship":"Located across the river from Siuwensin"},{"location":"Ovord Domain","relationship":"Alleged origin of foray guns"},{"location":"Commensal Border-Station","relationship":"Adjacent Commensal territory"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Siuwensin","arc":"Genly Ai's Mission and Orgoreyn Political Tensions","description":"An Orgota village on the Orgoreyn side of the Ey River bridge.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai and refugees are detained here after a raid, interrogated, and held in a storage-barn overnight.","relationships":[{"location":"Ey River","relationship":"Located across the river from Passerer"},{"location":"Passerer","relationship":"Source of the raiding foray"},{"location":"Commensal Border-Station","relationship":"Adjacent inspection point"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Commensal Border-Station","description":"An Orgote border checkpoint where Genly obtained a permiso for travel.","recentEvents":"Processed Genly's entry into Orgoreyn after verifying his credentials.","relationships":[{"location":"Siuwensin","relationship":"Adjacent to the Commensal Transient-House"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Ovord Domain","aliases":["Ovord Domain"],"description":"A Commensal region accused of supplying foray guns to Passerer.","recentEvents":"Whispers suggest Ovord Domain's involvement in the Siuwensin raid via foray guns.","relationships":[{"location":"Passerer","relationship":"Alleged supplier of foray weapons"},{"location":"Commensal Border-Station","relationship":"Adjacent Commensal territory"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Icefoot Lake","aliases":["Icefoot"],"description":"A frozen lake in Kerm Land where key events unfold.","recentEvents":"Young Estraven falls through the ice, is rescued by Therem of Stok, and later wounded during a hunt.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Part of Kerm Land"}]},{"name":"Ebos village","description":"A village on the north shore of Icefoot Lake.","recentEvents":"Estraven is taken here after being injured, then later the village sends people to retrieve Estraven's body.","relationships":[{"location":"Icefoot Lake","relationship":"Adjacent"}],"parentLocation":"Icefoot Lake"},{"name":"Rotherer Fastness","description":"A remote fastness where Therem of Stok resides for a year.","recentEvents":"Therem indwells here after being exiled, later returning to Estre as its new lord.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Part of Kerm Land"}]},{"name":"Artisan School","aliases":["Royal Workshop Foundry"],"description":"A central institution in Karhide where technological and artistic craftsmanship is practiced.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai mentions the ship's components are stored here after landing on Horden Island.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Part of"}]},{"name":"Horden Island","description":"A remote island where Genly Ai first landed on Gethen, serving as a temporary base for his mission.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai's arrival and subsequent departure from the island were discussed during conversations in Mishnory.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Linked via transportation"}]},{"name":"Hall of the Thirty-Three","aliases":["Thirty-Three Hall"],"description":"The assembly chamber where Orgote political debates occur.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai spoke here without public audience; Obsle played a tape of the session for Estraven.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Central political venue"}]},{"name":"Plastics Factory","description":"Estraven's workplace where he produces transparent boxes.","recentEvents":"Estraven works here during the day, reflecting on his exile and the Envoy's mission.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Industrial district"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Central Bureau Radio","description":"The Orgote government's communication hub controlling information flow.","recentEvents":"Estraven notes its role in suppressing news about the Envoy.","relationships":[{"location":"Sarf","relationship":"Operated by the Sarf"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Commensal Public Kemmerhouses","description":"Public venues for communal sexual activities and performances.","recentEvents":"Slose opposes obscene plays here, advocating for moral reform.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Social gathering spaces"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Pyenefen Street","description":"A commercial street where Gaum approaches Estraven.","recentEvents":"Gaum attempts to seduce Estraven, revealing Sarf surveillance.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Urban thoroughfare"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Meshe","aliases":["Center of Time"],"arc":"Gethenian Cultural Exploration","description":"A mystical location central to the narrative's philosophical themes, where Meshe perceives all time and existence simultaneously.","recentEvents":"Meshe's teachings about the Center of Time are recounted, revealing his prophetic visions of past, present, and future events.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"Meshe is a spiritual figure associated with Karhide's cosmology"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Tuerresh","description":"A region where the poor man of Sheney discovers a buried treasure, fulfilling Meshe's prophecy.","recentEvents":"The poor man excavates and finds ancient jewels, but Meshe foresees their eventual destruction and his own death.","relationships":[{"location":"Sheney","relationship":"Tuerresh is linked to the village of Sheney through the poor man's journey"}]},{"name":"Ornen Forest","description":"A vast, ancient forest housing a hemmen-tree with a secret leaf hidden in its darkness.","recentEvents":"Meshe plucks the hidden leaf from the tree, symbolizing the revelation of concealed truths.","relationships":[{"location":"Karhide","relationship":"The forest is part of Karhide's geography"}]},{"name":"Kundershaden Prison","aliases":["Kundershaden"],"description":"An old, grimy prison in Mishnory used for incarcerating political prisoners.","recentEvents":"Genly Ai was arrested here after being taken from Shusgis' house during a Yomesh festival.","relationships":[{"location":"Mishnory","relationship":"Located within the city"}],"parentLocation":"Karhide"},{"name":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","aliases":["Pulefen Farm","Third Voluntary Farm"],"arc":"Gethenian Cultural and Sexual Control","description":"A resettlement colony where Genly Ai and Estraven hide after escaping Karhide's political dangers.","recentEvents":"Genly and Estraven confront the consequences of Estraven's covert actions to safeguard Genly's mission.","relationships":[{"location":"Orgoreyn","relationship":"Site of Genly's temporary refuge and political maneuvering"},{"location":"Tarrenpeth Forest","relationship":"Surrounded by this forest"},{"location":"Sembensyens Mountains","relationship":"Bounded by these mountains"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Sembensyens Mountains","description":"A mountain range in Orgoreyn that the caravan-truck crosses during its journey.","recentEvents":"The truck crossed these mountains at over nine thousand feet during the night.","relationships":[{"location":"Pulefen Farm","relationship":"Boundaries include this mountain range"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Tarrenpeth Forest","description":"A vast, unpopulated coniferous forest in Orgoreyn's northwest, meticulously managed.","recentEvents":"The caravan-truck passed through this forest during its journey to the farm.","relationships":[{"location":"Pulefen Farm","relationship":"Surrounds the farm's perimeter"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Esagel River","description":"A river forming the southern boundary of the Pulefen Farm region in Orgoreyn.","recentEvents":"The Esagel River marks the southern edge of the farm's territory.","relationships":[{"location":"Pulefen Farm","relationship":"Bounded by this river"}],"parentLocation":"Orgoreyn"},{"name":"Ethwen","aliases":["Esagel Bay Port"],"description":"A gray port city built on the rocky shores of Esagel Bay, known for its rainy climate and seafaring population.","recentEvents":"The narrator buys trapping equipment and obtains a hunter's license here, planning to travel north.","relationships":[{"location":"Esagel River","relationship":"Located at the mouth of the river"},{"location":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","relationship":"Destination for the narrator's journey"}]},{"name":"Turuf","description":"A town along the Esagel River where the narrator temporarily resides and caches supplies.","recentEvents":"The narrator leaves the hunting party here, caches equipment, and returns to prepare for his escape.","relationships":[{"location":"Esagel River","relationship":"Located along the river's banks"},{"location":"Pulefen Farm","relationship":"Southward direction from the farm"}]},{"name":"Commensal Bureau","description":"An administrative office responsible for issuing licenses and permits for voluntary farms and trapping activities.","recentEvents":"The narrator acquires a hunter's license and authorization documents here.","relationships":[{"location":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","relationship":"Regulatory authority for the farm"}]},{"name":"Fire-Hills","aliases":["Fire Mountains"],"description":"A distant range of volcanic peaks known for their smoky plumes, located far to the north of Orgoreyn.","recentEvents":"Smoke from Udenushreke is observed, marking the narrator's approach to the region.","relationships":[{"location":"Udenushreke","relationship":"Part of the Fire-Hills range"}]},{"name":"Udenushreke","aliases":["Fire-Hill"],"description":"A specific volcanic peak within the Fire-Hills range, known for its persistent smoke and distant visibility.","recentEvents":"Smoke from this fire-hill is seen by the narrator during his journey north.","relationships":[{"location":"Fire-Hills","relationship":"A prominent feature of the range"}]}],"arcs":[{"name":"Genly Ai's Mission and Karhide-Orgoreyn Temporal Tensions","status":"active","characters":["Genly Ai","Therem Harth rem ir Estraven"],"summary":"Genly's physical endurance and adaptation to Gethen's harsh environment continue, with Estraven's covert aid ensuring their survival as they traverse toward the Ice, maintaining the unresolved geopolitical stakes."},{"name":"Estraven's Exile and Cross-National Political Strategies","status":"active","characters":["Genly Ai","Therem Harth rem ir Estraven"],"summary":"Estraven's strategic navigation of Gethen's terrain and resource management (pesthry hunting) sustains their journey, while political tensions between Karhide and Orgoreyn persist as they approach the Gobrin Glacier."},{"name":"Gethenian Cultural and Sexual Control","status":"active","characters":["Genly Ai","Therem Harth rem ir Estraven"],"summary":"Genly's psychological trauma and cultural disorientation persist, while Estraven's knowledge of the Handdara challenges systemic control, even as they physically escape the regime's reach."}],"summary":"Genly Ai and Estraven endure brutal winter conditions while traversing the Sembensyens Mountains, navigating rain-slicked slopes and hypothermic struggles. Their journey culminates at the Gobrin Glacier, a vast icy expanse that symbolizes both the physical and existential challenges of their mission. The glacier's presence underscores the harsh, desolate beauty of Gethen's northern landscape."},"model":"qwen3:8b","appVersion":"0.1.0"},{"index":19,"result":{"characters":[{"name":"Genly Ai","aliases":["Mr. Ai","the Envoy"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"15. To the Ice","currentLocation":"On the Ice, traveling through the forest towards the glacier","description":"The Ekumen's Envoy to Karhide, struggling with the political and psychological complexities of his mission.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Key figure in Genly's mission, later revealed as a political strategist"},{"character":"King Argaven XV","relationship":"The monarch he is attempting to persuade to join the Ekumen"}],"recentEvents":"Planned the glacier crossing route, discussed survival strategies, and prepared supplies for the journey"},{"name":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","aliases":["The King’s Ear","Lord Estraven"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"15. To the Ice","currentLocation":"On the Ice, traveling through the forest towards the glacier","description":"A nobleman from the Domain of Estre, known for his complex relationship with Genly Ai and his role in ending the feud between Estre and Stok.","relationships":[{"character":"King Argaven XV","relationship":"Formerly the king's closest confidant and advisor"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Allied through covert communication and financial support"},{"character":"Foreth rem ir Osboth","relationship":"Former kemmering (male companion)"}],"recentEvents":"Set traps for pesthry, provided sustenance for the journey, managed their sledge through extreme weather, and guided them toward the Gobrin Glacier."},{"name":"King Argaven XV","aliases":["the king"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"Royal House","description":"The paranoid and volatile ruler of Karhide, suspicious of foreign influence and internal dissent.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Formerly his most trusted advisor, now exiled"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"The Envoy whose mission he resists and interrogates"}],"recentEvents":"Child's birth and death, political speculation about succession"},{"name":"Pemmer Harge rem ir Tibe","aliases":["the king’s cousin"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"The king’s cousin and a member of the upper chamber, known for his rivalry with Estraven.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Rival and political adversary"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Interacted during the dinner conversation"}],"recentEvents":"Featured in news about Karhide’s territorial claims in the Sinoth Valley"},{"name":"servant","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"1. A Parade in Erhenrang","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A Karhidish servant who left after the meal.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Departed to their home after the meal, as Karhiders do not employ bonded labor."},{"name":"Getheren","aliases":["Ennoch"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"2. The Place Inside the Blizzard","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Brother who survived the exile and journey to the Ice, met his brother Hode in the Place Inside the Blizzard.","relationships":[{"character":"Hode","relationship":"Brother"}],"recentEvents":"Traveled to the Pering Ice, encountered Hode, died after returning to Shath and revealing his identity."},{"name":"Hode","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"2. The Place Inside the Blizzard","currentLocation":"The Place Inside the Blizzard","description":"Getheren's brother who committed suicide after being exiled, now resides in the Place Inside the Blizzard.","relationships":[{"character":"Getheren","relationship":"Brother"}],"recentEvents":"Died by suicide, appeared to Getheren in the Place Inside the Blizzard as a white, lifeless figure."},{"name":"the traveler","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"2. The Place Inside the Blizzard","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Carried Getheren's message back to Shath, confirming the domain's recovery after Getheren's death.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Received Getheren's final message and relayed it to Shath, contributing to the domain's restoration."},{"name":"Lord Berosty rem ir Ipe","aliases":["Ashe Berosty rem ir Ipe"],"importance":"main","status":"dead","lastSeen":"4. The Nineteenth Day","currentLocation":"Grende","description":"A nobleman who sought a Foretelling about his death and later killed his kemmering Herbor before dying by suicide.","relationships":[{"character":"Herbor of the Geganner clan","relationship":"kemmering"}],"recentEvents":"Received a Foretelling about his death, killed Herbor, and hanged himself on Odstreth."},{"name":"Herbor of the Geganner clan","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"dead","lastSeen":"4. The Nineteenth Day","currentLocation":"Grende","description":"A poor man who sought a Foretelling to save his kemmering Berosty rem ir Ipe.","relationships":[{"character":"Lord Berosty rem ir Ipe","relationship":"kemmering"}],"recentEvents":"Sought a Foretelling, was killed by Berosty, and died from the injury."},{"name":"Weaver Odren","aliases":["The Weaver","the Weaver","Faxe"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"13. Down on the Farm","currentLocation":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","description":"A Foreteller and the Weaver of the group, known for his role in the Foretelling sessions.","relationships":[{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Envoy and seeker of answers"},{"character":"the Inspector","relationship":"Aide"}],"recentEvents":"Administered drug examinations to Genly Ai and other prisoners."},{"name":"Goss","aliases":[],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"Otherhord","description":"A young Indweller who guides Genly Ai to the Fastness of Otherhord.","relationships":[{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Guide and companion"}],"recentEvents":"Led Genly Ai to Otherhord and engaged in conversation about the Handdara"},{"name":"the driver","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"on the caravan","description":"The driver of the landboats guiding the caravan through the Kargav.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Guided the caravan and shared stories about the Fastnesses"},{"name":"the physician from Spreve","aliases":["the physician"],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"5. The Domestication of Hunch","currentLocation":"Otherhord","description":"A physician from Spreve who entered the circle during the Foretelling session.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Entered the circle during the Foretelling session, contributing to the disruption of the session."},{"name":"the cook","aliases":[],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","description":"Guard at Pulefen Farm whose gun was stolen by Estraven.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Servant"}],"recentEvents":"Had his gun stolen by Estraven during the escape"},{"name":"the fisherman","aliases":[],"importance":"minor","status":"alive","lastSeen":"6. One Way into Orgoreyn","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"A fisherman who initially refused to help Therem","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Refused to assist Therem but later led to his capture"},{"name":"the Inspector","aliases":["Inspector"],"importance":"secondary","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Pulefen Commensality Third Voluntary Farm & Resettlement Agency","description":"A government official handling refugee interrogations and border controls.","relationships":[],"recentEvents":"Overlooked Estraven's escape due to his dothe-induced strength"},{"name":"Commensal Yegey","aliases":["Yegey"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Host at the lunch gathering, curious about the Ekumen.","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Maintains dependent relationship"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Host"}],"recentEvents":"Left Mishnor with Obsle, no longer in Genly Ai's trust"},{"name":"Commensal Obsle","aliases":["Obsle"],"importance":"main","status":"alive","lastSeen":"14. The Escape","currentLocation":"Unknown","description":"Commensal with political tensions regarding Estraven","relationships":[{"character":"Therem Harth rem ir Estraven","relationship":"Politically entangled"},{"character":"Genly Ai","relationship":"Interrogator"}],"recentEvents":"Left Mishnory with Yegey, no longer in Genly Ai's trust"},{"name":"Foreth rem ir Osboth","aliases":[],"importanc